"{\"uid\": \"newsweek.com-olympics-opening-ceremony-last-supper-muslim-leaders-response-1932766\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  Jul 31, 2024 at 02:20 PM EDT  updated  Jul 31, 2024 at 07:14 PM EDT  Reporter (Live News)  More religious leaderscontinue to condemnthe2024 Paris OlympicsOpening Ceremony for a scene involving drag queens that many viewers interpreted as a reference toThe Last Supper.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 151, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999857113751339, \"rank\": 0.00014290666814962543, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Friday's controversial display featured French DJ and LGBTQ+ icon Barbra Bush standing in the center of a long table, surrounded by fellow drag performers on either side of her.\", \"from\": 281, \"to\": 458, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 321, \"end\": 327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9994372411598724, \"rank\": 0.0005606327809432922, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 354, \"end\": 358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\", \"score\": 0.9992592770107491, \"rank\": 0.000740416550894601, \"text\": \"Bush\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The scene sparked widespreadcriticism from conservative Christiansclaiming it was offensive and disrespectful to Christian values and faith.\", \"from\": 459, \"to\": 599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 572, \"end\": 588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999985108772481, \"rank\": 1.4656905247019721e-06, \"text\": \"Christian values\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bush has since filed a legal complaint after receiving abuse online following the event.\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 688, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 600, \"end\": 604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\", \"score\": 0.9992592770107491, \"rank\": 0.000740416550894601, \"text\": \"Bush\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_W._Bush\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, The Olympic Games official X accounttweeted a photoof the scene, claiming, \\\"The interpretation of the Greek God Dionysus makes us aware of the absurdity of violence between human beings.\\\"\", \"from\": 690, \"to\": 886, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 801, \"end\": 806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"score\": 0.9999248693350786, \"rank\": 6.796506502638082e-05, \"text\": \"Greek\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_language\"}, {\"begin\": 811, \"end\": 819, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7482809446671226e-19, \"text\": \"Dionysus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dionysius_of_Halicarnassus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Tuesday, the supreme leader of Iran, Ayatollah Ali Khamenei, slammed the act for the \\\"insults\\\" against Jesus Christ in a statement postedto X.\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 1033, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 922, \"end\": 926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"score\": 0.9754569499234989, \"rank\": 0.024393376971906824, \"text\": \"Iran\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iran\"}, {\"begin\": 928, \"end\": 950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ali_Khamenei\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ayatollah Ali Khamenei\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ali_Khamenei\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ali_Khamenei\"}, {\"begin\": 938, \"end\": 950, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ali_Khamenei\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.441774536392917e-12, \"text\": \"Ali Khamenei\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ali_Khamenei\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ali_Khamenei\"}, {\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 1006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus_in_Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9255288112981601, \"rank\": 0.08046336753415256, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus_in_Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus_in_Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Respect for #JesusChrist ... is an indisputable, definite matter for Muslims,\\\" Khamenei, who has held his position since 1989, wrote.\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1105, \"end\": 1112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\", \"score\": 0.9999513514295724, \"rank\": 4.354010260326499e-05, \"text\": \"Muslims\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We condemn these insults directed at the holy figures of divine religions, including Jesus Christ.\\\"\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1256, \"end\": 1268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus_in_Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9255288112981601, \"rank\": 0.08046336753415256, \"text\": \"Jesus Christ\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus_in_Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus_in_Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During an address, Turkish President Recep Tayyi Erdo\\u011fan also spoke out against the ceremony, claiming he plans to callPope Francisright away to discuss the \\\"immorality committed against the Christian world.\\\"\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1480, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1291, \"end\": 1308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_Turkey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Turkish President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_Turkey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_Turkey\"}, {\"begin\": 1321, \"end\": 1328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Recep_Tayyip_Erdo\\u011fan\", \"score\": 0.9996948278673649, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Erdo\\u011fan\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Recep_Tayyip_Erdo\\u011fan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Recep_Tayyip_Erdo\\u011fan\"}, {\"begin\": 1463, \"end\": 1472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.6041139181595542, \"rank\": 0.65531693599557, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"disgraceful scene in Paris offended not only the Catholic world, not only the Christian world but also us as much as them,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1508, \"end\": 1513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999857113751339, \"rank\": 0.00014290666814962543, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1536, \"end\": 1544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 0.9999971530246111, \"rank\": 1.678133504834288e-06, \"text\": \"Catholic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 1565, \"end\": 1574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.6041139181595542, \"rank\": 0.65531693599557, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Immorality displayed at the opening of the Paris Olympics once again highlighted the scale of the threat we face.\\\"\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1735, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Al-Azhar, the top institution of the Sunni branch of Islam in Egypt, said in a statement, \\\"The scenes portray Jesus \\u200eChrist in an offensive image that involves disrespect to his person.\\\"\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1923, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1774, \"end\": 1779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunni_Islam\", \"score\": 0.9960121489022076, \"rank\": 0.0040038177267227495, \"text\": \"Sunni\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunni_Islam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sunni_Islam\"}, {\"begin\": 1799, \"end\": 1804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\", \"score\": 0.99999444547526, \"rank\": 5.548706336083693e-06, \"text\": \"Egypt\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egypt\"}, {\"begin\": 1847, \"end\": 1852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus_in_Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9479406655729933, \"rank\": 0.054917739063347626, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus_in_Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus_in_Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Al-Azhar, and nearly 2 billion Muslims behind it, believe that Jesus ... is the \\u200eMessenger of Allah.\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 2026, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1957, \"end\": 1964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\", \"score\": 0.9999513514295724, \"rank\": 4.354010260326499e-05, \"text\": \"Muslims\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\"}, {\"begin\": 1989, \"end\": 1994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus_in_Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9479406655729933, \"rank\": 0.054917739063347626, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus_in_Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus_in_Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Quran reads, Jesus is Allah's 'Word through Mary and a spirit \\u200efrom him,'\\\" the statement referenced Islam's religious book.\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2031, \"end\": 2036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quran\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.575637866309512e-31, \"text\": \"Quran\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quran\"}, {\"begin\": 2044, \"end\": 2049, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus_in_Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9479406655729933, \"rank\": 0.054917739063347626, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus_in_Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus_in_Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 2075, \"end\": 2079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_in_Islam\", \"score\": 0.9999999894021131, \"rank\": 1.0501556049237603e-08, \"text\": \"Mary\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q2566598\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_in_Islam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_in_Islam\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Muslim Council of Eldersgrand imam of Al-Azhar also issued a released statement on the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 2156, \"to\": 2264, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This disgraceful act showed a complete lack of respect for the beliefs of religious people and the high moral values they hold dear,\\\" it read.\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2409, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The council unequivocally rejects all attempts to demean religious symbols, beliefs, and sacred figures.\\\"\", \"from\": 2410, \"to\": 2516, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Sunday, a spokesperson for the Paris Olympics, Anne Descamps, told the media thatThe Last Supperdisplay was not meant to be offensive and defended the vision of the ceremony's artistic director Thomas Jolly.\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2573, \"end\": 2581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}, {\"begin\": 2715, \"end\": 2721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"score\": 0.6946458385520131, \"rank\": 0.43958250073294197, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Clearly there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2821, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"On the contrary, I think (with) Thomas Jolly, we really did try to celebrate community tolerance,\\\" Descamps said.\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2922, \"end\": 2930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Looking at the result of the polls that we shared, we believe that this ambition was achieved.\", \"from\": 2937, \"to\": 3032, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If people have taken any offense we are, of course, really, really sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Jolly toldThe Associated Pressafter the ceremony, \\\"My wish is not to be subversive, nor to mock or to shock.\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3217, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of all, I wanted to send a message of love, a message of inclusion and not at all to divide.\\\"\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3316, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you have a storyNewsweekshould be covering?\", \"from\": 3318, \"to\": 3364, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you have any questions about this story?\", \"from\": 3365, \"to\": 3408, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Contact LiveNews@newsweek.com  \\u00a92025Newsweek Digital LLC\", \"from\": 3409, \"to\": 3465, \"entities\": []}]}"